TEXT.S: = Panital = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Cwosisyang ka alang Panital. 127 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 427 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 95% niqan 406 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 5% niqan 21 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun86%, Amis4%, Paiwan1%, Truku1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq1%, ni rahuq na o1%.
